title: How to sing like a Grammy award singer
description:
Learn the inside music industry secret of the technique and exercise they use in developing an originality in their voices that  stand out of the crowd and set them all in a class of their own as platinum recording artists!



Speech Level Singing makes singing as natural and easy as speaking. Used by more than 120 Grammy winners and developed by Seth Riggs, legendary vocal coach to the stars, SLS produces an effortless, powerful and expressive voice.This audio program has 30 lessons of speech level singing exercises with Seth rigg!
